	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喲，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<pageBreak />我有陣子沒跟你聊天啦。<delay20 />
