<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我想你有自己的事要處理，<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但你也別努力過頭啦？<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
